Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:40.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}看吧枯叶起舞 终会化为蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}然后调节到位
