Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:47.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}时过境迁太急 秒速开始不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全因自己武断的选择开端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以必须做出了断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:55.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无聊的理由 是停止思考的铁证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:01:59.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无法守护应守护之物 那就不要乱出头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:03.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共鸣 荣光 称赞 都不应奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:07.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不明真相的引力 将常识归于虚无
