Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善善恶恶都无法评议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:26.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全都变得讨厌 连这都是幸福的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不行 不要说得如此悲凉 世界依然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:33.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}即使你会哭泣也还活着
